        "Region": 3,
        "CharacterDialogInfo_List": [
          {
            "CharacterId": 10101,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1010101,
            "DisplayOrder": 570,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 5950,
            "LocalizeKR": "종연 후의 객석은,\n쓸쓸한 것이군.",
            "LocalizeJP": "終演後の\n客席というのは、\n寂しいものだな。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_01_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10101,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1010101,
            "DisplayOrder": 580,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 11050,
            "LocalizeKR": "그 많던 관객은 빠지고,\n조명은 모두 꺼지고…",
            "LocalizeJP": "大勢いた観客がはけ、\n照明はすべて消えて…",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10101,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1010101,
            "DisplayOrder": 590,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7750,
            "LocalizeKR": "화려한 무대는\n흔적도 없이,\n정적에 잠겨 있다.",
            "LocalizeJP": "華やかなステージは\n跡形もなく、静寂に\n沈んでいる。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10101,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1010101,
            "DisplayOrder": 600,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 15750,
            "LocalizeKR": "열기와 함성으로 가득했던 공간이\n갑자기 조용해지니… 어딘가,\n애틋한 느낌마저 든다.",
            "LocalizeJP": "熱気と歓声に\n満ちていた空間が\n突如静まると…どこか、\n切なさを覚えるほどだ。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10101,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1010101,
            "DisplayOrder": 610,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 11100,
            "LocalizeKR": "…그래도 지금은 괜찮다.",
            "LocalizeJP": "…でも、今はもう、\n大丈夫だ。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10101,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1010101,
            "DisplayOrder": 620,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 11100,
            "LocalizeKR": "변한 것은 아무것도 없지만,\n평온하게 있을 수 있다.",
            "LocalizeJP": "変わったことは\n何もないが、\n穏やかでいられる。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10101,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1010101,
            "DisplayOrder": 630,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 12100,
            "LocalizeKR": "…선생님이\n옆에 있으니까,\n일지도 모르겠군.",
            "LocalizeJP": "…先生が隣にいるから、\nかもしれないな。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_05_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
